    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong> new Beverage-Air installation (specialty installer trade through Ali Group authorized dealers); sister Ali Group brand equipment outside refrigeration (Scotsman ice machines, Ice-O-Matic, Champion dishwashers, Carpigiani gelato are separate trade categories with their own service paths); chain corporate facility service contract management (we work as approved local contractor with chain regional managers, but we don't manage the corporate contracts themselves).</p>

    <p>For warranty-eligible repairs, we document the failure on-site, the operator processes the claim through Ali Group North American distribution (4 to 7 day standard part ship), and we install the replacement.</p>
