    <p class="lead">Diagnostic is $120 (commercial tier), waived with the repair. Beverage-Air OEM parts on critical components (fan motors, compressors, defrost heaters, control boards). Sourced through Ali Group North American distribution with 4 to 7 day standard ship; expedite available.</p>

